#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.241"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.241:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.241:0.2"
msgid "25. Duccaritavagga"
msgstr "25. Bad Conduct"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.241:0.3"
msgid "241. Paṭhamaduccaritasutta"
msgstr "241. Bad Conduct (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.241:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā duccarite."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of bad conduct."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.241:1.3"
msgid "Attāpi attānaṃ upavadati;"
msgstr "You blame yourself."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.4"
msgid "anuvicca viññū garahanti;"
msgstr "After examination, sensible people criticize you."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.5"
msgid "pāpako kittisaddo abbhuggacchati;"
msgstr "You get a bad reputation."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.6"
msgid "sammūḷho kālaṃ karoti;"
msgstr "You feel lost when you die."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.7"
msgid ""
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"And when your body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a place of loss, "
"a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an5.241:1.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā duccarite."
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks of bad conduct."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.241:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā sucarite."
msgstr "There are these five benefits of good conduct."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.241:2.3"
msgid "Attāpi attānaṃ na upavadati;"
msgstr "You don’t blame yourself."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.4"
msgid "anuvicca viññū pasaṃsanti;"
msgstr "After examination, sensible people praise you."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.5"
msgid "kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati;"
msgstr "You get a good reputation."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.6"
msgid "asammūḷho kālaṃ karoti;"
msgstr "You don’t feel lost when you die."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.7"
msgid "kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When your body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a good place, a "
"heavenly realm."

msgctxt "an5.241:2.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā sucarite”ti."
msgstr "These are the five benefits of good conduct.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.241:2.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
